    • Field Detail

      • feature_selector_panel

        public FeatureSelectorPanel feature_selector_panel
        A panel allowing the user to select features to extract from symbolic music files and extract the features. Basic feature parameters may be set and feature values and definitions can be saved to disk.

      • recording_selector_panel

        public RecordingSelectorPanel recording_selector_panel
        A panel allowing the user to select files to extract features from.

        Symbolic music files may also be played here.
